parameters: \nc<>H-How was it? Did it come across properly?

\nc<>Yes, that's right. The believers I met earlier were all
warm and nice people.

\nc<>...! So, that's right! I'm glad... Sometimes, I felt sad
when the citizens looked at me with disdain.

\nc<>(It's not flattery. At least from the impression so far,)
(It feels more like a sincere local community rather than a
religion.)

\nc<>(However, I'm concerned about that area where you can't go
unless your contribution level is high...)

\nc<>So, um, regarding that, have you made up your mind about
joining the Paradise Church...?
\nc<>May I ask if it's okay to ask if I can ask you something...?

\nc<>I see. First, I should try meeting this so-called religious
leader...

\ncY-You're the ones blocking the way, right!? Move aside
quickly! I-I don't want to be brainwashed...!
\nc<>Oh my, you're saying strange things, aren't you?

\nc<>(Is this man the leader of the Paradise Church...?) (...For
now, it seems he's not a villain, but I wonder if that's
really the case.)

\nc<>Mobo-san. There are other believers and customers here.
Please come back to the meditation room.

\nc<>Sigh... I guess there's no other choice. Since it's come to
this--
\nc<>Please wait. Please let this man go.
\nc<>Oh, are you here to visit the Paradise Church?

\nc<>Welcome... or at least, that's what I would like to say,
but the situation isn't very favorable, is it?

\nc<>Please don't glare at him so much. Besides, he was planning
to send that man back from the beginning.

\nc<>Of course. There wouldn't be a church that would imprison
someone just because they snuck out during worship these
days.

\nc<>In the first place, what we were doing in there was just
regular meditation.

\ncN-No way! They definitely tried to mesmerize me with some
strange light!
\nc<>Our motto is to reach out a helping hand to those in need.

\nc<>Sometimes, there are people who don't have the luxury to
accept a helping hand.

\nc<>If you're not convinced no matter what, Kei-san can
personally bring that man to you.
\nc<>Then, I'll take you up on your offer.

\nc<>This is unfortunate timing for today. First impressions are
important after all.

\nc<>Ah... If you become interested in the Paradise Sect again,
please do ask me about the process of meditation.
\nc<>It's sad to end things misunderstood, you know.
\nc<>I obtained the memory N2: Paradise Sect.
